{"tid":1642274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一位律師朋友的提醒","createTime":"2019-10-09T15:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T16:37:55.000Z","uid":248458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4dcd57be1d72885f440f8f7c10f2ae782bc763","tid":1642274,"uid":248458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"一位律師朋友的提醒<br />\n<br />\n當如果你身邊有人被捕拉咗入差館的時候, 佢會循例問你攞個人資料又稱三世書.<br />\n<br />\n依家有個人資料被洩漏, 打去公司投訴, 話嗰間公司有員工參與暴動! 不斷發酵和滋擾<br />\n<br />\n當然冇證明係警方說, 但係都已經係好明顯嘅事<br />\n<br />\n所以無論如何被捕之後, 都唔可以講任何野! 保障自己! 直到有律師陪同下為止, 大家係有權乜都唔講包括最普通的個人資料<br />\n<br />\n請大家一定要保障自己個人私隱 吾好俾人有機會去騷擾！"},{"pid":"e90c6ecfc70d0509ad9be1c7ee5c12fadd91e123","tid":1642274,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"Tuii"},{"pid":"753ee173d22b6504e74b449a99e3e7fdd1e5dbd3","tid":1642274,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdRkv9K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdRkv9K.png&h=9458928b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de775ae2e2681b6719599bc418deb728671ae0d9","tid":1642274,"uid":248458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:37:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"120593cdf93dd706c57f1b78f4dcd0a3df7690bb","tid":1642274,"uid":248458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}